description: KORE Mining Ltd. engages in the exploration, development, and evaluation of mineral resource properties. It focuses on two 100% owned gold projects, including the Imperial project that consists of 654 claims covering an area of approximately 31,000 acres located in Imperial County, southeastern California; and the Long Valley gold development project that cover an area of approximately 15,965 acres located in Mono County, east-central California. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
